social_posts.post_text: Mama is officially inside ♥️. Once feral, now friendly.  Asking for prayers that her Tues Vet visit comes out all clear!

Her first 24hrs have been nothing short of a miracle.  Mama has been calm, happy and sweet.  Seeing her enjoy her first nap on a comfy bed like the queen that she is makes me happier than I’ll ever be able to express.
It’s a beautiful thing to watch her relax in peace
Enjoy my haul!…you know where to find the links

What a wonderful afternoon we had 🥰🥰 it was amazing to visit with our dear friends Noosha and Navid ♥️ Matt cooked up a storm today!  We enjoyed great food and dessert, had a birthday celebration and some laughs.  The cats loved all the attention, especially from D &D! 🐈‍⬛ This visit meant the world to us ♥️. The boys were a pleasure and you all are welcome anytime on Long Island.  We love you guys and truly missed you.  Until next time, my Texas friends xo Safe travels
Mama is doing well
Cutest manicure I’ve had in a minute 🥰 Jenny is the best 😎

I saw this today and LOVE it. You have to enjoy people who watch your everyone move just to be angry that they aren’t you or have your life.  Put all your energy into having your best life 💕💕

It’s been 5 weeks now with Mama inside.  Now, only while I’m present, I open the door for everyone to see eachother.  No hissing, growling or attacking so I’m hopeful.  Mama will remain quarantined for quite some time but I think she is looking forward to her new family.  She can sense there is no aggression here….
Loving my beautiful manicure by @jenny_zhuang.q 💅
I found my old pics on an external hard drive that I thought were long gone tonight…thousands of pics of us…we were babies here…

My cute little batboy…. #simon #blackcat #halloween #lucky It’s funny that this arrived today because at 4am today we had a bat get into our house but we safely got it out the window with my stealthy moves 💪🏻😎
When the sky is illuminated from lightning and Simon is interested in watching.  I haven’t seen a thunderstorm with lightning like this in a long time.
Just sharing my recent haul!  If it’s not your thing, that’s cool, look away 🤣

For those of you asking, Mama is doing great.  She is still in her own bedroom and I think she is going to be in there a long time.  That’s ok, she is a feral girl, now friendly, but still wild.  She has her own space, gets personalized attention and is happy .  My girl put on a little weight which is good as she needed to.  Mama is thriving.
Oh August….where is the time going?  Hope everyone had a nice weekend 🥰 #nomakeup #readyforbed
Well, I woke up today and I’m 44.  Yesterday’s hair, no makeup and a hoodie…hoping the sun comes out but it’s not looking good for that ☁️ At least I get to enjoy some oysters later with my love.

Ended my day doing laundry in my newly renovated laundry room.  These @lgusa machines are elite and so quiet.  I’m so happy @loweshomeimprovement came through with fast delivery when @bestbuy cancelled.  I am thoroughly impressed.  Thank you all so much for the birthday wishes. It means the world to me, more than I can express. ♥️💕. 43 was the year of change, 44 is the year of healing and happiness 💕

Happy National feral cat day!!! I couldn’t let today pass without acknowledging my very own feral turned family girl Mama.  These pictures are of her first day inside and today!  It took 6 years and a lot of patience to bring this girl in…She has thrived beyond what we could have ever hoped for.  We love you Mamas!!!
Now THIS is a combo of dreams! Boogie and Gordon #squishmallows
I’m seriously missing my babies tonight. ♥️♥️ they were the two best feline companions anyone could ever ask for ♥️♥️

So this weekend I fell down the stairs, and fell outside of a subway…that’s was fun… I’m pretty banged up but the magic cuddling powers of Sashimi have helped heal me, a little…It was a strange few days
Do you all see who is out and about!??????

Mama on my unmade bed with her new family!  Everyone seems unbothered and coexisting which is all I have hoped for! Mama even got up and laid next to Bibbles to spy to Sasha. #rescue #feral #ignoremypatchedwall

Who said you can’t pull full glam in a hoodie and messy ponytail? Hahahahah. Had a great visit with an old friend I haven’t seen since high school last night, so many laughs…and I woke up feeling like myself, light, happy and rested.  Laughter really is the best medicine ♥️♥️
My girls helping me pack ♥️♥️♥️
From my bed, unedited.  Open drawers, messy countertop and clean laundry piled up…no need to stage the scene, this is everything 😄
Self care has a face 🤣🤣🤣

I’m so proud of this girl.  It’s been 5 months since we brought her in off the streets and she grows more confident every day.  Mama sleeps with me every night now and has found comfort amongst her peers.  I wouldn’t say they are all besties yet, but definitely coexisting…it’s ok, we all know how besties can treat you in the end anyways 😂😂😂😂
Good night everyone!

I completely stand by this.  I have always been the friend to others that I’ve wanted for myself.  I seek love, trust, loyalty, compassion, comfort, support and full disclosure without judgment.  I believe you should always strive to be who you would want to be around.  I am blessed to have a hand full of ladies in my life who know me and love unconditionally, including all the poop talk.  Thank you all for being my blessings.

This girl right here was the first best friend I ever had.  We met our first day of junior high in 1991 and is still my girl.  Who would have thought that 7th grade art class would bring a 33 year friendship that has lasted the test of time.  She knows me through and through, all my dark secrets, and some of the most iconic core memories I have stored involved her.  I love you always Jackie. “Eat me”

Had a late #NYE lunch with my love and now we are home for the night! I want to wish everyone a happy and blessed New Year.  In 2024 I will be focusing on my family,  friends, new endeavors and my cats!  Life is too short to focus on those who don’t love and appreciate you for who you are, tasks that don’t make you happy and activities that stress you.  New year, Same Samantha but upgraded goals.  Thank you all for your continued support and loyalty through 2023 and into 2024 we go…. If you have goals or resolutions please feel free to share them below, I’d love to support you.

On the drink menu tonight…. @chef_zollvineyards delicious Spiced Blackberry Sangria with fresh mango, pineapple and honey crisp apple as well as @malibu_rum also with fresh mango, pineapple and honey crisp apple.  Fun fact, I grew up with the amazingly talented Frank Zoll, founder of Zoll Vineyards.  I have now tried 5 of his wines, cider and sangrias, all of which are sublime. (He has many more on his roster though). I have tagged him in this post if you want to try them out, I promise you won’t be disappointed.  He is also a lovely person which I am happy to support and I hope you will too! (All available on this website zollvineyards.com ) #happynewyear #wine #localbusiness #virgjnia #love #notsponsored #paidforbyME
